[TestInitCmdHelp - 1]
Scaffold a new Kubernetes project in the specified directory.

  Includes:
  - 'ksail.yaml' configuration file for configuring KSail
  - 'kind.yaml'|'k3d.yaml'|'talos/*' configuration file(s) for configuring the distribution
  - '.sops.yaml' for managing secrets with SOPS (optional)
  - 'k8s/kustomization.yaml' as an entry point for Kustomize

Usage:
  init [flags]

Flags:
  -d, --distribution string          Kubernetes distribution to use (default "Kind")
  -f, --force                        overwrite files
  -h, --help                         help for init
  -o, --output string                Output directory for scaffolded files (default ".")
  -r, --reconciliation-tool string   Reconciliation tool to use (default "Kubectl")
  -s, --source-directory string      Directory containing workloads to deploy (default "k8s")

---

[TestInitCmdExecute - 1]
Scaffolding new project
✔ project scaffolded

---